title: Chairman Mehaffie's Support For Arts Merits Award (Edison Community College)
text: ( Source : Edison Community College ) Darryl Mehaffie, with wife Mary Ann , is the recent recipient of the prestigious William L. Combs Patron of the Arts Award , given in recognition of Mehaffie's significant contribution to the Arts. Edison
